Text: Acadian Asset Management LLC lifted its stake in shares of Travelzoo by 25.6% in the second quarter. Acadian Asset Management LLC now owns 278,986 shares of the information services provider's stock valued at $4,307,000 after buying an additional 56,926 shares during the period.
